race.comment: MIRA BALE (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (26.65) at Geelong behind Gunai Daisy in a Grade 5. Got back and turned spotting a start but found the line impressively. Can find winning form. PAW CASSIAN (2) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (26.21) at this track. Has ability and is one of the better chances. BUCK SHINES (4) ran good time (25.74) when placing two back at Shepparton but missed the frame latest in a Grade 5 at Shepparton. Can find the frame this time. MORE VOLTAGE (1) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.
